item.title: Eddys First Trip
item.description: A bit of a shake down run in Eddy and what seemed a very long drive through Dublin we arrive in Kilfenane Where we will spend our first night. Turned out to be an new aire at the back of a Bar so after Tea we had a pint. Lotti {{ more }} After breakfast, and on to Cork where we meet with Karen, walked Lotti and Coffeed in Blackrock Castle.
